  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three women killed, 18 injured in accident in Muthur",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three women were killed and 18 others were injured when the tractor they were travelling in skidded off the road and toppled over at Pachchanoor in Muthur this morning.",
        "The tractor was travelling on a hilly road carrying building materials and a group of women at the time of the accident.",
        "Police said the driver of the tractor and 20 women who were traveling in were injured and were admitted to the Muthur Hospital.",
        "Three women in critical condition had died on admission to the Hospital.",
        "Police said the group met with the accident while they were traveling for construction work in a temple in the area."
      ],
